501
00:30:53,036 --> 00:30:54,037
Beleza.

502
00:30:55,079 --> 00:30:56,789
Admita logo, Sam!

503
00:30:59,542 --> 00:31:00,960
Tá bom, fui eu!

504
00:31:01,044 --> 00:31:02,962
